title: Abstract Line Art
description: A simple abstract design featuring a white line that forms a corner shape against a black background.

title: Geological Cross-Section
description: An illustrated geological cross-section showing a landscape with mountains, valleys, and a river. The upper part depicts a vibrant green environment with mountains in the background, a winding river, and lush vegetation. The lower part reveals a cross-section of the earth, showcasing geological layers, including rock formations and a fault line.

title: Simple Geometric Shape
description: A minimalist design featuring a white line forming a corner shape on a black background.

title: Mountain Landscape
description: A breathtaking aerial view of a mountain with steep cliffs, surrounded by lush greenery and a blanket of clouds at the base. The sunlight illuminates the rocky surface, highlighting the textures and colors of the landscape.

title: Aerial View of a Highway and Tunnels
description: An aerial view of a winding highway that features two tunnels. The road curves gracefully through a mountainous landscape, with greenery on one side and a construction area on the other. The scene captures the contrast between natural terrain and human engineering.

title: Mountainous Landscape with Boulders
description: A scenic view of a mountainous landscape featuring large boulders scattered across the foreground. The background showcases rugged mountain peaks under a clear blue sky, with patches of greenery and rocky terrain visible.
